window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In a world of superheroes, supervillains, mystical portals, and monsters from strange realms, I'd be considered perfectly ordinary, living a normal life in an extraordinary world.</p> <p>That is until fate intervened.</p> <p>A simple act alters and enhances me into a stratosphere of unfathomable power. I'll navigate unique powers, cultivate my strength, progress through unusual skills, and become one of a cosmic order of defenders called Mana Storms.</p> <p>Can I learn and cultivate my power before an ancient evil awakens to consume my world?</p>"; 
